<item>
            <title>[WICKET-5522] Failing HTTPS redirect to RequireHttps annotated pages with ONE_PASS_RENDER strategy</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/WICKET-5522</link>
                <project id="12310561" key="WICKET">Wicket</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Activated JS: Start the quickstart -&amp;gt; Press the submit buttons -&amp;gt; See the secured page with https!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Deactivates JS: (NoScript Firefox Plugin): Start the quickstart -&amp;gt; Press the submit buttons -&amp;gt; See the secured page BUT with HTTP!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;There was no proper https redirect.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;If I change the rendering strategy to REDIRECT_TO_BUFFER everything works fine, but if I change the strategy to ONE_PASS_RENDER the https forwarding does&apos;t work anymore. But only if I deactivate all scripts...&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Regards,&lt;br/&gt;
Dmitriy&lt;/p&gt;</description>
